    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You can exploit your opponent’s tells in the heat of battle to gain an edge in defeating them.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Sense Motive 3 ranks</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You can study your opponent using Sense Motive as a move action. The DC is 15 + 1-1/2 × the target’s CR and the creature must have an Intelligence score of 3 or higher. On a success you either gain a +2 insight bonus to your next attack of opportunity against that foe or gain a +1 insight bonus to AC against the next attack from that foe, whichever occurs first before the start of your next turn.</p>"
    },
